  ---
  
  ### ğŸ“¤ Response (Output)
  
  **Success Response (200 OK):**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "post (slug) updated successfully",
    "data": {
      "message": "post (slug) updated successfully",
      "post": {
        "id": 72,
        "title": "Updated Title",
        "slug": "new-post-slug",
        "content": "Updated content here...",
        "summary": "Updated summary",
        "featuredImage": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
        "indexed": 1,
        "published": 1,
        "createdAt": "2026-01-19T10:30:00.000Z",
        "editedAt": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z",
        "authorId": 1
      }
    },
    "timestamp": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z"
  }
  ```
  
  **Post Not Found (404 Not Found):**
  ```json
  {
    "success": false,
    "message": "post (slug) not found",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z"
  }
  ```

  **Slug Conflict (409 Conflict):**
  ```json
  {
    "success": false,
    "message": "slug already exists",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z"
  }
  ```
  
  **Unauthorized (401):**
  ```json
  {
    "success": false,
    "message": "Unauthorized",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-19T18:39:21.316Z"
  }
  ```
  
  ### Notes
  
  - Only provided fields are updated
  - Requires admin authentication
  - Updates editedAt timestamp automatically
  - `slug`: Must be lowercase letters, numbers, and hyphens only. Returns 409 if slug already exists.
  - `indexed`: Controls SEO indexing (0 = not indexed, 1 = indexed)
  - `published`: Controls visibility (0 = draft, 1 = published)
